title: Fighting Is Magic Collection
description:
All games in zip archives, unpack and play. Also works with Wine.
     
1.leaked - first leaked version, not modded and without AI.
2.evostorm - modification by Evost0rm: modded leaked version with AI and new stages.
3.iwanabrawl - mod by Iwanabrawl: added Fluttershy and Rainbow Dash, hard AI, boss, new stages, rebalancing, support network game.
